Subject: NEA-Varonis Battle Card
Description:
Hey team, how are you doing?

We got asked by a possible client, if it's possible, to elaborate a kind of battle card with indications of what NEA can do over Varonis, mainly on users permissions on File System.

The question was: "Varonis have the functionality to change permissions of monitored users, can NEA do the same?"

If you can send me some documentation, if possible, that shows some details on this subject, it would be great

Thank you!
